perfSONAR_PS::Collectors::LinkStatus README File
==================================

Description
-----------

perfSONAR_PS::Collectors::LinkStatus is a module that provides the ability to
collect link status information and store it in an MA.

Installation
------------

 CPAN installation
 -----------------

    perl -MCPAN -e 'install perfSONAR_PS::Collectors::LinkStatus'

 Standard installation
 ---------------------

    Prerequisites:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

